line_1: Ev'n godly meetings o' the saunts,
line_2: Thou art the life o' public haunts;

line_1: Ev'n godly meetings o' the saunts,
line_2: But thee, what were our fairs and rants?

line_2: When gaping they besiege the tents,

line_1: Ye mak a devil o' the Saunts,
line_2: Ye hae sae monie cracks an' cants,
